        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>By opting into SMS communications from Jassar Trans LLC, you agree to the terms outlined below. Please read these terms carefully before proceeding. These terms apply to all SMS communications you receive from us, including appointment updates, order notifications, and more.</p>

        <h3>Types of Messages You Will Receive</h3>
        <p>By subscribing to our SMS service, you will receive various types of messages including but not limited to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Appointment Scheduling:</strong> Updates regarding your transportation services, including scheduling and confirmations.</li>
            <li><strong>Order Alerts:</strong> Notifications about the status of your shipments and deliveries.</li>
            <li><strong>Account Notifications:</strong> Important updates related to your account activity with Jassar Trans LLC.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Messaging Frequency</h3>
        <p>The frequency of messages may vary depending on your interactions with our services. You may receive messages related to your appointments, shipments, or other important notifications, especially when there are updates or actions required.</p>

        <h3>Message and Data Rates</h3>
        <p>Standard message and data rates may apply. Please check with your mobile carrier for details on your messaging and data charges. Your mobile service provider may charge for text messages and data usage in accordance with their terms and rates.</p>

        <h3>Opt-Out Instructions</h3>
        <p>If you no longer wish to receive SMS notifications from Jassar Trans LLC, you can opt-out at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any SMS message you receive from us. This will prevent you from receiving further SMS messages.</p>

        <h3>For Assistance</h3>
        <p>If you need help or further information regarding your SMS service, simply text <strong>HELP</strong> to any message you receive. Alternatively, you can visit our website or contact us directly.</p>

        <h3>Agreement</h3>
        <p>By opting into SMS communications through any form or method provided by Jassar Trans LLC, you are consenting to receive SMS messages in accordance with these terms and conditions. Please keep in mind that message frequency may vary, and data charges may apply.</p>

        <p>For additional information on our privacy practices, please see our <a href="privacy-policy.html">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
